reviewText: What is there to say? You are either a fan or you're not. And, you will never get to see it on Saturday mornings now.

My son is very into sharks. My husband watched this show and asked me to look it up on Amazon and see if it was available. My son was so excited when they came in the mail. He's watched them over and over several times!

i love kenny the shark. he is one of the best cartoon characters in the universe and beyond! he is one of my all time favorites!
